										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="1"><strong>葡萄</strong></p>
<p data-track="2">是很多人都爱吃的水果</p>
<p data-track="3">每到葡萄成熟的季节</p>
<p data-track="4">在水果店能看到</p>
<p data-track="5">各个品种的葡萄</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-542" title="8f4fc811162e46aaa3ded3323a26428d" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/8f4fc811162e46aaa3ded3323a26428d.jpg" alt="8f4fc811162e46aaa3ded3323a26428d" width="639" height="426" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">紫色、绿色、黑色、红色……</p>
<p data-track="7">一颗颗晶莹剔透</p>
<p data-track="8">不仅甜美多汁</p>
<p data-track="9">葡萄还有非常多的</p>
<p data-track="10"><strong>营养价值和功效哦！</strong></p>
<p data-track="11"><strong>不同颜色葡萄的营养价值</strong></p>
<p data-track="12"><strong>◎ 红葡萄：</strong></p>
<p data-track="13">含逆转酶，可软化血管、活血化瘀，防止血栓形成，心血管病人不妨多吃。逆转酶在红葡萄皮里含量最丰富，最好连皮一起吃。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-544" title="49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda.jpg" alt="49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda" width="1056" height="764" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda.jpg 1056w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda-300x217.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda-1024x741.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/49a1c36b2144472cab3370fbe7574fda-768x556.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1056px) 100vw, 1056px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="14"><strong>◎ 绿葡萄：</strong></p>
<p data-track="15">功效偏重于清热解毒。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-543" title="2e0c378b2f954cb484d2c37a93350f5a" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/2e0c378b2f954cb484d2c37a93350f5a.jpg" alt="2e0c378b2f954cb484d2c37a93350f5a" width="748" height="512" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/2e0c378b2f954cb484d2c37a93350f5a.jpg 748w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/2e0c378b2f954cb484d2c37a93350f5a-300x205.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="16"><strong>◎ 紫葡萄：</strong></p>
<p data-track="17">富含花青素，可以美容抗衰老。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-545" title="b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9.jpg" alt="b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9" width="1104" height="752" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9.jpg 1104w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9-300x204.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9-1024x698.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/b1ac83ca2c214f36833ce959da5b5bc9-768x523.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1104px) 100vw, 1104px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="18"><strong>◎ 黑葡萄：</strong></p>
<p data-track="19">可滋阴养肾，使头发更黑亮。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-547" title="af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b.jpg" alt="af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b" width="1080" height="768" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b.jpg 1080w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b-300x213.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b-1024x728.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/af146f7280714204b4bbec18927dba2b-768x546.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="20"><strong>好处多多：葡萄的功效</strong></p>
<p data-track="21"><strong>☆ 阻止血栓形成</strong></p>
<p data-track="22">葡萄能降低人体血清胆固醇水平，降低血小板的凝聚力，对预防心脑血管病有一定作用。</p>
<p data-track="23"><strong>☆ 提神抗疲劳</strong></p>
<p data-track="24">葡萄中的葡萄糖、有机酸、氨基酸、维生素对大脑神经有兴奋作用，常食对神经衰弱和过度疲劳者也有益处。</p>
<p data-track="25"><strong>☆ 祛痰消炎</strong></p>
<p data-track="26">长期吸烟者可多吃葡萄。葡萄既可帮助肺部细胞排毒，又具有祛痰作用，可缓解吸烟引起的呼吸道发炎、痒痛等症状。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-546" title="8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf.jpg" alt="8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf" width="1068" height="764" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf.jpg 1068w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf-300x215.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf-1024x733.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/8edd19215efa4defa501c09adaf7ddaf-768x549.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1068px) 100vw, 1068px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="27"><strong>☆ 减肥美容</strong></p>
<p data-track="28">葡萄是吃了不容易发胖的水果。女性每天食用十来颗含有大量维生素的新鲜黑葡萄或绿葡萄，既能达到减肥目的，又有益于心血管健康。</p>
<p data-track="29"><strong>☆ 抗癌</strong></p>
<p data-track="30">葡萄含有一种抗癌微量元素(白藜芦醇)，可以防止健康细胞癌变，阻止癌细胞扩散。是抗氧化的绝佳食物。</p>
<p data-track="31">尽管有不少功效</p>
<p data-track="32">但是<strong>以下的注意事项</strong></p>
<p data-track="33"><strong>需要牢记</strong></p>
<p data-track="34"><strong>食用葡萄的注意事项</strong></p>
<p data-track="35"><strong>1. 脾胃不和、虚寒洁泻者慎食</strong></p>
<p data-track="36">葡萄性寒凉，脾胃不和、虚寒洁泻者应慎食用。</p>
<p data-track="37"><strong>2. 葡萄和牛奶不要同时食用</strong></p>
<p data-track="38">葡萄会强化肠胃的酸度，牛奶难以消化吸收，严重者还有可能导致腹泻。</p>
<p data-track="39"><strong>3. 吃完葡萄不要立即喝水</strong></p>
<p data-track="40">吃葡萄后立刻喝水，不到一刻钟可能会引起腹泻。因为葡萄与水、胃酸急剧氧化、发酵，加速肠道蠕动，就会产生腹泻。</p>
<p data-track="41"><strong>入膳疗效佳：葡萄的养生妙用</strong></p>
<p data-track="42"><strong>葡萄熘凤脯</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-548" title="ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634.jpg" alt="ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634" width="1092" height="604" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634.jpg 1092w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634-300x166.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634-1024x566.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ee4181272bf5490c9e2924c9fa160634-768x425.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1092px) 100vw, 1092px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="43">原料：鸡脯肉 200g、无核鲜葡萄 100g，葱姜米 各适量，淀粉 20g、蛋清 1个</p>
<p data-track="44">做法：将鸡脯肉切成1.5cm见方的丁，加精盐、蛋清、淀粉上浆；葡萄在开水中稍烫后取出剥去皮待用。炒锅上火入油，烧至四成热，倒入鸡丁滑油至断生后捞出。锅中留底油，煸香葱姜米，加汤少许，调以精盐、料酒、白糖、味精、白胡椒粉、香醋，勾芡后倒入鸡丁及葡萄，淋油翻匀装盘即成。</p>
<p data-track="45">功效：滋阴补血，清热生津。</p>
<p data-track="46"><strong>蜂蜜葡萄</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-549" title="65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08.jpg" alt="65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08" width="1144" height="768" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08.jpg 1144w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08-1024x687.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/65fdbc6f82cf45b385c54dfc439a9b08-768x516.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1144px) 100vw, 1144px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="47">原料：葡萄 500g、蜂蜜 适量</p>
<p data-track="48">做法：将鲜葡萄洗净、挤汁，用陶器加水适量，置于火上，先武火煮沸，再文火煎煮汁液，去渣取汁，熬稠，加入蜂蜜服用之，每次服用1食匙。</p>
